<br />\n但佢唔同朱經緯<br />\n佢唔駛上前線<br />\n所以最多都係決策失誤<br />\n或監管不力"},{"pid":"fb78a4c51ffe0f612c53620b7c62d2d7178a585b","tid":1435023,"uid":43739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T16:20:42.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}